&lt;p>&lt;em>&amp;rsquo; I feel as if I&amp;rsquo;m losing all my leaves. The branches, and the wind, and the rain. I don&amp;rsquo;t know what&amp;rsquo;s happening anymore.&amp;rsquo; -&lt;/em> Anthony (&amp;lsquo;The Father&amp;rsquo;)&lt;/p>&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://compossible.asym-intel.info/images/uploads/2024/03/tree.webp" alt="">&lt;/p>
&lt;hr>
&lt;p>Struggling wordlessly into the light&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Startling eruption of limb&lt;/p>
&lt;p>As green as green has ever been&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Flowing and fumblingly growing&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Out of dark moist cloister&lt;/p>
&lt;hr>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://compossible.asym-intel.info/images/uploads/2024/03/as-green-as-green.webp" alt="">&lt;/p>
&lt;hr>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>Hail Mary&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Blessed is the fruit&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Of thy womb&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Pray for us now1&lt;/p>
&lt;hr>&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://compossible.asym-intel.info/images/uploads/2024/03/hail-mary.webp" alt="">&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>